data.description: Oh my goodness, what a cutie! Welcome to 1016 Valley Ave, a charming and well-located home in the heart of Knoxville, TN. This property presents a fantastic opportunity for homeownership or a savvy investment at an attractive price point.  Featuring 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, this delightful home, described as ''cute as a button,'' offers 837 square feet of living space, ensuring comfort and convenience for its occupants. The character of this older home shines through with it's charming front porch and  beautiful hardwood floors that add warmth and a timeless appeal to the interior spaces. A unique spiral staircase not only serves as a functional element of the home but also as an eye-catching design feature, adding a touch of elegance and creativity leading to the upper bonus area.  The upper bonus area (NOT included in overall square footage) has heat and air and easily could be finished into an additional room or used as a storage area. The home sits on a level yard, providing plenty of open space for outdoor activities and relaxation.  Don't miss your chance to own this charming house located in vibrant South Knoxville.  The location is very convenient to downtown Knoxville, restaurants, hospitals, the University of Tennessee, and the interstate. And don't forget about nearby South Landing Park at the waterfront. With its blend of aesthetic appeal, practicality, and strategic location, it's a property that offers both immediate enjoyment or a great long term income producing property.  Whether you are a first time home owner, student, downsizing, or looking to invest, this home offers an unmatched blend of comfort, charm, and convenience. Schedule your appointment today!  SHOWINGS BEGIN APRIL 20 (Roof 11/2019, new HVAC, water hater, and dishwasher.  Hardwoods under kitchen flooring)
